{"tid":1777222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網民擬黃昏時段發起「和你展」　工展會冀勿滋擾市民","createTime":"2019-12-10T05:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T03:18:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7c92658fb121d349e53f0282c1d04c64e417d8","tid":1777222,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"工展會第一天開鑼，有網民計劃於黃昏時段發起「和你展」活動。廠商會第二副會長兼展覽服務有限公司主席徐晉暉形容，工展會是「香港人的工展會」，對活動表示歡迎，不過呼籲參與人士不要對其他市民造成太大滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n徐晉暉指，沒有就網民計劃的活動特別向警方作出相應協調，不過他提到，過往有扒手出現工展會會場時，也會有警員進入會場範圍，強調今屆工展會也不能阻止警方進場執法。<br />\n<br />\n若果展覽期間交通狀況有異，他希望相關政府部門可以協助疏導人群。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496911-20191210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496911-20191210.htm&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=13335d49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496911-20191210.htm&h=713a78d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496911-20191210.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1496911_1_20191210130420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1496911_1_20191210130420.jpg&h=97831a4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fd144fa7bf1c666eb596cc13415d7930fe0ef21","tid":1777222,"uid":188482,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"比8蚊入去叫下口號 之後藍絲廢老抵唔住頸撩交打 再有防暴黎 之後提早關門 手足就安全撒退  睇下邊個蝕得甘d"},{"pid":"5bff91c23db6ff3c48f7efdec3dd3bd9f03170bc","tid":1777222,"uid":47149,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9466b65a1eb9302fc67faa6ec4206dc313904d1","tid":1777222,"uid":230537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"我唔撚係市民？"